price: (69) I had no knowledge of the exalted assembly [of angels] when they were disputing [the creation of Adam].
arabic: مَا كَانَ لِيَ مِنۡ عِلۡمِۭ بِٱلۡمَلَإِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰٓ إِذۡ يَخۡتَصِمُونَ
